00:23:48,895 --> 00:23:49,552
Vivian?

477
00:23:49,555 --> 00:23:51,528
Maaf, Jendral, aku akan menghubungi kembali.

478
00:23:51,531 --> 00:23:52,646
Tamuku sudah datang.

479
00:23:52,649 --> 00:23:54,815
