496
00:24:33,773 --> 00:24:35,105
Itu dia syaratnya.

497
00:24:35,453 --> 00:24:37,691
Kami membaca beberapa teori
yang kau posting di internet.

498
00:24:37,886 --> 00:24:39,943
Zombie? Sungguh?

499
00:24:40,497 --> 00:24:41,945
Kau boleh tertawa,

500
